title: Ep. #66 | SEVENTEEN, BLACKPINK, Sunmi
description:
This week, Eric reviews some "hot & sexy" new K-pop releases: 'Left & Right' by SEVENTEEN, 'How You Like That' by BLACKPINK, and 'pporappippam' by Sunmi.


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
